{"id":571945,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【图说天朝】不忘初心-牢记使命/","date":"2017-11-13T08:02:17Z","modified":"2017-11-13T08:02:17Z","title":"【图说天朝】不忘初心 牢记使命","content":"<p>@游研社：【网易“吃鸡”手游进行了一次更新 “大逃杀”变“军事演习”】网易某“吃鸡”手游进行了更新，更新后游戏变成了维和部队“军事演习”的主题，开始界面能看到“不忘初心、牢记使命、刻苦训练、磨砺成才”“维护国家安全、维护世界和平”等横幅。官方表示这是为了作品传递理念符合中华民族传统文化习惯 ​。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggl2jnuj21040k7goa.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571948\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggl2jnuj21040k7goa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggl2jnuj21040k7goa.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggl2jnuj21040k7goa-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggko2s0j21050koq6d.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571947\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggko2s0j21050koq6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"252\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggko2s0j21050koq6d.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggko2s0j21050koq6d-300x172.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggq0t6tj21120kunpd.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571951\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggq0t6tj21120kunpd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggq0t6tj21120kunpd.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggq0t6tj21120kunpd-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggke615j21120kutsl.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571946\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggke615j21120kutsl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggke615j21120kutsl.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggke615j21120kutsl-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggm5cflj21120kub29.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571949\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggm5cflj21120kub29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggm5cflj21120kub29.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggm5cflj21120kub29-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggnl9m3j21120ku1kx.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571950\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggnl9m3j21120ku1kx.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggnl9m3j21120ku1kx.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/9d0d09ably1flgggnl9m3j21120ku1kx-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>@慢半拍先生史蒂夫钟：大吉大利，守护党旗。</p>\n<p>@Twe12e：非常你国了可以说。</p>\n<p>@夏洛伊de风：我就记得有人说，一来都是空血，玩家互相发射加生命的子弹，直到血满了，就离开游戏，那个设定超级好。</p>\n<p>@DeGrace小陀螺：也就你国喜欢这样做表面功夫了。实则人人都心知肚明但总要装着点。</p>\n<p>@我和荷包蛋打起来了：建议出个开箱系统，稀有掉落红军套，长征系列。</p>\n<p>@瑞虎儿i：太多的宣传让人反感。</p>\n<p>@cd99：一下子就变成了正能量主旋律红色大作……</p>\n<p>@铁锈的福音使：一个文化自信的国。</p>\n<p>@L我讨厌秘密：角色不是中国人差评，不能选少数民族差评！</p>\n<p>@sr_no：社会主义朋克。</p>\n<p>@ReGelg：强国吃鸡，崛起了！</p>\n<p>@笑道人丶：绝地求生之解放军大比武。</p>\n<p>@亲幂关系-LC祝专辑大麦：而且还有标语一直伴随到你落地</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/75472591gy1flggot9hktj21kw16onpd.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-571952\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/75472591gy1flggot9hktj21kw16onpd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/75472591gy1flggot9hktj21kw16onpd.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/75472591gy1flggot9hktj21kw16onpd-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@两个半馒头：广电：不错不错，不维护社会主义核心价值观的游戏不是好游戏。</p>\n<p>@那个剑纯：毒气弹随机落在地图某点，然后向四周扩散，比跑动速度快，然后玩家互射“爱的子弹”来加血，好感动。</p>\n<p>@觉得自己很帅的魏二狗：只感觉到恶心。</p>\n<p>@天元无极限：不是，这么干真的很恶心人啊。这让玩家怎么玩？</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B221%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E4%B8%93%E5%88%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE/\">【图说天朝】新时代中国特色社会主义</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/%E5%A5%87%E5%AE%A2%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF-%E5%B9%BF%E7%94%B5%E6%80%BB%E5%B1%80%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%83%E6%9D%80%E7%B1%BB%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/\">奇客资讯 | 广电总局表示不会批准大逃杀类游戏</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[12013,9160,13379,11741,33519,9249,9254,11392,26544,25890,32729,9707,24636]}